            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Transmission ionisation chamber for measurement",
                "the incident proton current.  The chamber was",
                "recalibrated at each energy point."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "AMS"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Cl-36 identification was achieved with a Bragg",
                "detector  using P10 gas and Cl-35,37 isotope tails were",
                "suppressed using a Wien velocity filter.",
                "Each sample was measured 3-5 times, corrected for",
                "fractionation and dead-time and then normalised to",
                "Cl-36/Cl standard.  Where applicable, ratios were  also",
                "carefully corrected for effects of varying and",
                "excessive S-36 rates which cause integrated Cl-36 rates",
                "to be enhanced above their true value.  Error",
                "propagation included a 5% reproducibility  uncertainty,",
                "a 1-6% statistical uncertainty and a 0-10% uncertainty",
                "in calculating the correction factor due to S-36",
                "interference."
              ]
            }
          ],
